          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Razor Blades <span class="texto2">by <a href="../../issue10/lina_meruane/bio.php" class="link3">Lina Meruane</a>, Translated by Lina Meruane in collaboration with <a href="../../issue10/ronald_christ/bio.php" class="link3">Ronald Christ</a></span></td>
